ontent/uploads/2024/11/dsc09931-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09931.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不会占用太多空位</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276215" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09930-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09930-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09930.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲盒内有硬身垫保护耳机</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276350" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09954-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09954-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09954.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可有效保护耳机</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276348" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09956-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09956-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09956.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另设软身便携袋</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1276222" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09934-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09934-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09934.jpg 1280w" sizes